Cut to SECRETARY OF DEFENSE and SCOOTER LINDLEY sitting on a bench.
SCOOTER LINDLEY is holding the overthruster and covering the
SECRETARY OF DEFENSE with his M-14.

SECRETARY OF DEFENSE:
