BUCKAROO BANZAI grins at PERFECT TOMMY and walks away.
PERFECT TOMMY looks upset.  RENO NEVADA punches his shoulder.

RENO NEVADA:
        Awwwww....
        

BUCKAROO BANZAI walks up to the bus.  NEW JERSEY is standing at the door. 
